# Packaging build artifacts (generated by the npm/pypi builds; never committed).
# The committed source of truth is the contract instances + tools/ generators +
# the generated bindings under gen/. These dirs are produced by `npm run build` /
# `python -m build` and must NOT enter the tree.

# npm (@molecule-ai/contracts)
node_modules/
dist/
package-lock.json
*.tgz

# pypi (molecule-ai-contracts)
build/
dist_py/
*.egg-info/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
